msgstr "Centuries later, people still reach for pen and paper when a text won't do."

#: src/features/seasonal-events/events/lyrids.tsx:114
msgid "Chinese records from 687 BC describe \"stars falling like rain\" — the oldest known account of the Lyrids, and one of the oldest documented meteor observations of any kind."
msgstr "Chinese records from 687 BC describe \"stars falling like rain\" — the oldest known account of the Lyrids, and one of the oldest documented meteor observations of any kind."

